Decorator pattern :

1. Beverage is the base class
2. It has few types, 
	a.) Espresso
	b.) HouseBlend
	c.)	Decaf
3. Any coffee can have multiple flavours.
    a.)hazelnut
    b.)mocha
    c.)whip
    d.)soy


Make wrappers and pass instances of original object into it.

Beverage beverage = new HouseBlend();
beverage = new Soy(beverage);
beverage = new Mocha(beverage);
beverage = new Whip(beverage);
